comment: Nene (HOU) makes marginal contact with Westbrook (OKC) that does not affect his SQBR.
Gordon (HOU) makes contact with the ball and the part of Oladipo's (OKC) hand that is considered part of the ball.
Grant (OKC) allows Beverley (HOU) to land following the jump shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact with Harden (HOU) during the rebound.
Harden (HOU) and Westbrook (OKC) make incidental contact with one another during the rebound.
Oladipo (OKC) commits a take foul on Nene (HOU).
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact with Nene (HOU) off ball.
Nene (HOU) obtains a legal guarding position but the contact with Westbrook (OKC) is marginal.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harden (HOU) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Beverley (HOU) makes marginal contact with Adams (OKC) attempting to defend Westbrook (OKC) around the screen. Adams makes contact with Westbrook on the jump shot attempt.
Gordon (HOU) makes marginal contact with Abrines (OKC) that does not affect his FOM during the inbound.
There is no conclusive video evidence that Gordon (HOU) makes contact to Westbrook's (OKC) arm on the jump shot attempt.
Nene (HOU) commits a take foul on Adams (OKC).
[Observable in enhanced video] Adams (OKC) steps over the plane of the free throw line prior to the ball hitting the rim.
Grant (OKC) makes contact to Nene's (HOU) body that affects his shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) pushes off Abrines (OKC) to create space during the inbound.
RATR shows that Adams (OKC) and Ariza (HOU) make incidental foot to foot contact with another.
Westbrook (OKC) commits a take foul on Gordon (HOU).
